 size-full\"><img src=\"http://rcdi.gov.bf/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/APHRC-Logo-notext.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-75\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"66.66%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Le Centre africain de recherche sur la population et la santé est la première institution de recherche et groupe de réflexion du continent, produisant des preuves pour conduire l\'action politique visant à améliorer la santé et le bien-être des Africains.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>En tant que centre de recherche mondial progressiste dirigé par des Africains investi dans la création . . . <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" target=\"_blank\">En</a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" target=\"_blank\"> </a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" target=\"_blank\">s</a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" target=\"_blank\">a</a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" target=\"_blank\">v</a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" target=\"_blank\">o</a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" target=\"_blank\">i</a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://aphrc.org/who-we-are/\" target=\"_blank\">r</a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"h